Paper: hep-th/9707243

Date: 1997-07-29

Title: A Note on a Class of Cosmological String Backgrounds

Comments: 7 pages, latex

Journal-ref: JHEP 9812 (1998) 024

We study a class of four dimensional, anisotropic string backgrounds andanalyse their expansion and singularity structure. In particular we will seehow O(3,3) duality acts on this class.